section.heading: Exemptions—Health maintenance organization, health care service contractor, certified health plan

content.p: Print RCWs > Title 82 > Chapter 82.04 > Section 82.04.322 82.04.321 << 82.04.322 >> 82.04.323 PDF RCW 82.04.322 Exemptions — Health maintenance organization, health care service contractor, certified health plan. This chapter does not apply to any health maintenance organization, health care service contractor, or certified health plan in respect to premiums or prepayments that are taxable under RCW 48.14.0201 . [ 1993 c 492 s 303 .] NOTES: Findings — Intent — 1993 c 492: See notes following RCW 43.20.050 . Short title — Savings — Reservation of legislative power — Effective dates — 1993 c 492: See RCW 43.72.910 through 43.72.915 .
